    <h2>
      <a href="/episodes/372-bullet">Bullet</a>
      
    </h2>
    <div class="description">
      Bullet will notify you of database queries that can potentially be improved through eager loading or counter cache column. A variety of notification alerts are supported.
      <span class="stats">(6 minutes)</span>
    </div>
    <div class="watch">
        <a href="/episodes/372-bullet?autoplay=true" class="pretty_button">Watch Episode</a>
        <a href="/episodes/372-bullet?view=asciicast" class="pretty_button read_button">Read Episode</a>
    </div>
